人證明咗我只係想買店主整嘅水晶耳環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總結: 我終於沉冤得雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>到底你嘅on9到底係扮定真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條女今日仲扮無野正常咁sell佢d耳環出story 扮曬蟹 以為唔表態就可以扮乜事我都冇發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢宜家搞到到某d小店無得做生意 自己就搵大錢又買名牌 仲成日係ig share自己用咩化妝品同護膚品 當正自己係kol<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要濫用自己人氣去叫d followers report人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見打手咁有heart總結曬d point 咁我都唔執輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總括而言，<a href=\"http://tide.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftide.hk&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=ea6134e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tide.hk</a>店主罪行如下：<br />\n1.對客態度差 唔應機 <br />\n2.做野劣 甩色甩扣<br />\n3.賣假水晶 <br />\n4.食水深 <br />\n5.抄襲淘寶扮自己無抄 <br />\n6.屈人抄襲 打壓小店<br />\n<br />\nany肥 其實根本無人咁得閒想攻擊佢 係佢自撩者賤 得罪太多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢個請勿抄襲64週以嚟開咗接近50個story去狙擊小店 <br />\n到今時今日先有人嚟爆佢d衰野 已經好俾面佢 話曬佢都賺到夠曬<br />\n累到苦主咁慘 篇澄清就咁1句話個耳環秘密網同佢唔關事就想算? <br />\n<br />\n總結：<br />\n相信tide店主一定有mon住呢個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你一日唔道歉唔del精選 總會有人同你玩盡佢 唔好諗住深潛就無野 <br />\n你覺得你有好多客唔睇連登就諗住扮無野? 大把苦主同你ig見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上個post有絲打總結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed568a91f7909ee5b07bf23a111b16ec7ea49368","tid":2497683,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afd87ba79581f07a59f12ca60a5d77471f8a03da","tid":2497683,"uid":348618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bd25f7ddbb1b0c687e3f7c